states <- map_data("state")
ggplot()+
  geom_polygon(data= states,
               aes(x= long,
                   y= lat, 
                   group= group,
                   fill = region))+
  geom_point(data= filtered_bigfoot,
             aes(x= longitude,
                 y= latitude),
             color="black",
             alpha = 0.5)+
  facet_wrap(~season)+
  labs(x= "Longitude",
       y= "Laditude",
       title= "Sight Spottings of Bigfoot in America Excluding Alaska")+
  theme(legend.position = "none")
